<c.white><c.mono_sans>We're the fugitives,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1305
00:39:19.983 --> 00:39:21.776 position:42.38%,start align:start size:25.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>not you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1306
00:39:21.818 --> 00:39:22.819 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
