1309
00:39:24.237 --> 00:39:27.448 position:40.48%,start align:start size:27.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>nor mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1310
00:39:27.490 --> 00:39:30.702 position:21.43%,start align:start size:65.24% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Professor Lang, however minor</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1311
00:39:27.490 --> 00:39:30.702 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>her role in this matter,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

