00:39:55.476 --> 00:39:56.769 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>if you'd taken my advice</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1332
00:39:56.811 --> 00:39:58.938 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and not gotten involved</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1333
00:39:56.811 --> 00:39:58.938 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
