<c.white><c.mono_sans>Ah, that alone</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1398
00:41:43.460 --> 00:41:46.587 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You heard the man.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1399
00:41:43.460 --> 00:41:46.587 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Get moving.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1400
00:41:46.629 --> 00:41:47.755 position:27.14%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Thank you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1401
00:41:50.091 --> 00:41:51.217 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Both of you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1402
00:41:51.259 --> 00:41:53.470 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes, yes, yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1403
00:41:51.259 --> 00:41:53.470 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Go, go, and quickly.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1404
00:41:53.511 --> 00:41:55.221 position:38.57%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Keep up the good work.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1405
00:42:13.114 --> 00:42:16.868 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Quark, I've got</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1406
00:42:13.114 --> 00:42:16.868 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to say good-bye.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1407
00:42:16.909 --> 00:42:18.786 position:27.14%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Oh, just let them go.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1408
00:42:18.828 --> 00:42:20.413 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It'll be less painful that way.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1409
00:42:20.455 --> 00:42:24.459 position:32.86%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, you don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1410
00:42:24.501 --> 00:42:27.545 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have to say good-bye to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1411
00:42:28.629 --> 00:42:30.215 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm going with them.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1412
00:42:30.256 --> 00:42:32.091 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But we had a deal.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1413
00:42:32.133 --> 00:42:33.968 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can't stay here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1414
00:42:34.010 --> 00:42:38.097 position:23.33%,start align:start size:65.24% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Maybe one day I can come back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1415
00:42:34.010 --> 00:42:38.097 position:23.33%,start align:start size:61.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and we'll be together again</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1416
00:42:38.139 --> 00:42:40.517 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but not until my work is done.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1417
00:42:40.558 --> 00:42:42.768 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So, all I have to do</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1418
00:42:40.558 --> 00:42:42.768 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to get you back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1419
00:42:42.810 --> 00:42:45.855 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is wait until Cardassia becomes</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1420
00:42:42.810 --> 00:42:45.855 position:19.52%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a free and democratic society?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1421
00:42:49.650 --> 00:42:52.153 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I promise...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1422
00:42:52.195 --> 00:42:54.364 position:51.90%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll make it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1423
00:42:52.195 --> 00:42:54.364 position:51.90%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>worth the wait.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1424
00:43:06.834 --> 00:43:10.796 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I could come with you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1425
00:43:06.834 --> 00:43:10.796 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't suppose</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1426
00:43:10.838 --> 00:43:14.633 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, it's not your fight.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1427
00:43:14.675 --> 00:43:16.844 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Besides, I could never</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1428
00:43:14.675 --> 00:43:16.844 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>live with myself</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1429
00:43:16.886 --> 00:43:18.846 position:25.24%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>if something happened to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1430
00:43:18.888 --> 00:43:22.267 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I need to know that</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1431
00:43:18.888 --> 00:43:22.267 position:44.29%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you're here, safe.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1432
00:43:22.308 --> 00:43:25.811 position:30.95%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That way, a part of</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> me</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1433
00:43:22.308 --> 00:43:25.811 position:30.95%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>will always be safe, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1434
00:43:35.196 --> 00:43:36.864 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, Quark.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1435
00:43:38.616 --> 00:43:40.201 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I always will.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1436
00:43:56.175 --> 00:43:57.718 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1437
00:44:01.389 --> 00:44:05.017 position:19.52%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I suggest we return</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1438
00:44:01.389 --> 00:44:05.017 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to the Promenade without delay.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1439
00:44:06.478 --> 00:44:09.355 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You have to tell me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1440
00:44:06.478 --> 00:44:09.355 position:42.38%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Why did you do it?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1441
00:44:09.397 --> 00:44:10.565 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Shoot Toran.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1442
00:44:10.607 --> 00:44:13.067 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well, why did you let</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1443
00:44:10.607 --> 00:44:13.067 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Professor Lang go?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1444
00:44:13.109 --> 00:44:15.653 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have no choice.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1445
00:44:13.109 --> 00:44:15.653 position:48.10%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love her.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1446
00:44:15.694 --> 00:44:17.696 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I love Cardassia,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1447
00:44:17.738 --> 00:44:19.991 position:19.52%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>which is why</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1448
00:44:17.738 --> 00:44:19.991 position:19.52%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had to do what I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1449
00:44:22.285 --> 00:44:24.912 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1450
00:44:24.954 --> 00:44:27.081 position:19.52%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's the thing about love.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1451
00:44:27.123 --> 00:44:29.792 position:19.52%,start align:start size:34.76% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No one really</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1452
00:44:27.123 --> 00:44:29.792 position:19.52%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>understands it, do they?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

